<view class="calender">
  <view class='calender-week'>
    <block wx:for="{{cWeekText}}" wx:key="{{index}}">
      <view class='week-item'>{{item}}</view>
    </block>
  </view>
  <block wx:for="{{monthData}}" wx:key="{{index}}" wx:for-item="monthItem" wx:for-index="monthDataIndex">
    <view class='calender-nav'>
      <view class='calender-nav-text'>{{monthItem.currentYear}}年{{monthItem.currentMonth}}月</view>
    </view>
    <view class='calender-days {{selectType == "checkbox"?monthDataIndex==firstTap.monthIndex||monthDataIndex==lastTap.monthIndex?"is-checkbox-active":"":""}} {{selectType == "radio"?monthDataIndex==firstTap.monthIndex?"is-radio-rctive":"":""}}'>
      <block wx:for="{{monthItem.currentMonthData}}" wx:key="{{index}}">
        <view class='days-item {{selectType == "checkbox"?monthDataIndex==firstTap.monthIndex?index==firstTap.dayIndex?"is-checkbox-first-active":"":"":""}} {{selectType == "checkbox"?monthDataIndex==lastTap.monthIndex?index==lastTap.dayIndex?"is-checkbox-last-active":"":"":""}} {{selectType == "radio"?index==firstTap.dayIndex?"is-radio-both-active":"":""}} {{monthDataIndex==0?index<monthData[0].activeIndex?"disabled":"":""}} {{selectType == "checkbox"?firstTap.monthIndex==lastTap.monthIndex?monthDataIndex==firstTap.monthIndex?index>firstTap.dayIndex&&index<lastTap.dayIndex?"checkbox-disabled":"":"":firstTap.monthIndex<lastTap.monthIndex?monthDataIndex==firstTap.monthIndex?index>firstTap.dayIndex?"checkbox-disabled":"":monthDataIndex==lastTap.monthIndex?index<lastTap.dayIndex&&index>=monthItem.dayOneIndex?"checkbox-disabled":"":"":"":""}}' data-dayindex='{{index}}' data-year='{{monthItem.currentYear}}' data-month='{{monthItem.currentMonth}}' data-monthindex='{{monthDataIndex}}' catchtap='{{monthDataIndex==0?index<monthData[0].activeIndex?"":"daysItemTap":"daysItemTap"}}'>{{item}}</view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>



<!--
  calender-days的view里的cclass解析：
  1.{{selectType == "checkbox"?monthDataIndex==firstTap.monthIndex||monthDataIndex==lastTap.monthIndex?"is-checkbox-active":"":""}}
  判断是否是checkbox类型，是的话就继续判断，不是的话就不做操作。如果是则继续判断哪个月份，然后给点击的月份添加is-checkbox-active类

  2.{{selectType == "radio"?monthDataIndex==firstTap.monthIndex?"is-radio-rctive":"":""}}
  判断是否是radio类型，是的话就继续判断，不是的话就不做操作。如果是则继续判断哪个月份，然后给点击的月份添加is-radio-rctive类
-->
